						               													<description>Loot Pirates is a pirate-themed party game where the players point guns at one another in order to divvy up the pirate loot.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each player takes the role of a pirate crew with one player acting as captain.  Each round, the captain calls out &amp;quot;Ready!  Set!  Aim!&amp;quot; and players simultaneously point their guns at each other in order to acquire their targets doubloons.  Players parlay and negotiate in order not to get shot.  Alternatively, they may run away.  Any pirates left standing at the end of the round get a share of the booty.  Gameplay continues until the loot is all divvied up.  The pirate with the most loot at the end of the game wins and becomes captain for the next game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
